Once you unsubscribe you won't be charged again, but you are responsible for whatever charges have already been incurred during your current billing cycle. For example, if your billing cycle is on the 18th of every month, and you cancel on the 29th, you won't be charged again come the 18th of the following month, but you will not be refunded any prorated portion of your current billing cycle.
